Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{sent it flying with tremendous force,}{\i0}sau đó phun thẳng vào đồng xu,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{hit the coin mid-air,\Nand when it was floating...}{\i0}bắn trúng nó trên không trung...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{he sucked the coin up\Nusing the power of his lungs alone!}{\i0}sau đó dùng mồm hút nó về...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Wait, is that what I saw?}{\i0}Khoan đã... cái quái gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Interesting.}Thú vị lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That was close.}Nguy hiểm quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What was a person doing\Nlying on the floor there anyway?}Cơ mà sao tên này lại nằm dưới sàn nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{He's unconscious.\NBetter get him there quickly.}Bất tỉnh luôn rồi. Phải đưa đến phòng y tế ngay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What the... I'm human again.}{\i0}Mình... đã trở lại thành người.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:06.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I can't remember anything that happened\Nafter I was turned into a doll.}{\i0}Không thể nhớ khi mình bị biến thành rối...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{How the hell did I...}{\i0}Rốt cuộc chuyện gì...
