Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:13.07,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{BAM BAM BAM BAM}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Wh-What the hell are you doing!?}M-Mày làm cái quái gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Working my exterior obliques.}Luyện tập cơ sườn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oh... Okay.}À ừ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Wait, the fact that you're here\Nmeans you brought me...}Cơ mà mày ở đây tức là đã đưa tao đến hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's right.}Chính xác.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Why?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I was your enemy.}Tao là kẻ thù của mày mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Well...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{When one of us is in trouble,\Nwe're all in tr—}Khi gặp rắc rối thì phải giúp đỡ--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:43.94,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{BITE}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mhy tohnge... Nearly bit it off...}Lưỡi tôi... cắn trúng rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I-I see.}V-Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Okay, I'm going now.}Rồi, tôi đi đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Take care of yourself.}Anh giữ gìn sức khoẻ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Huh? Sure.}Hả? À ừ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{When one of us is in trouble,\Nwe're all in trouble, huh?}Khi gặp rắc rối thì giúp đỡ nhau à...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Damn that punk.}Thằng khốn...
